===Etymology===
Of [[Moorish]] origin, from Arabic {{ARchar|[[كراء|الكراء]]}} (''al-kirā’''), rent, rental, hire, lease. [http://buscon.rae.es/draeI/SrvltGUIBusUsual?LEMA=alquiler].

===Noun===
